# Project Overview

This is a CRM system focused on appraisals and customer management with integrations to various Google Cloud services.

## Main Components

- **Entry Point**: [index.js](mdc:index.js) - Initializes all services and sets up Express routes
- **Database Schema**: [prisma/schema.prisma](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) - Defines all data models and relationships
- **API Routes**: 
  - [src/routes/customers.js](mdc:src/routes/customers.js) - Customer management endpoints
  - [src/routes/email.js](mdc:src/routes/email.js) - Email interaction endpoints

## Key Services

- **Database**: PostgreSQL via Prisma ORM
- **Storage**: Google Cloud Storage for image uploads
- **Email**: SendGrid integration for customer communications
- **AI**: OpenAI integration for appraisals and processing
- **Messaging**: Google PubSub for event handling

## Architecture

The application follows a modular architecture with separate services for different functionalities. The main service initializes all other services and sets up API routes.
